{"tid":1302002,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"各位即將放榜既朋友 我有野想講","createTime":"2019-07-09T20:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T02:18:06.000Z","uid":71930,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf192c5c08f01b315ece250c0a9e2a231da20ae","tid":1302002,"uid":71930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:23:11.000Z","msg":"希望放榜既你唔會好似我當年咁straight 3敗走入asso<br />\n但我想講 聽日無論點都好<br />\n你地都已經好叻好叻 打咗埸靚仗<br />\n所以無論你咩分都好 唔洗灰心<br />\n冇人同你傾 好驚好失落既 就上黎連登搵人傾<br />\n連登唔要再失去任何一個巴絲<br />\n即使要讀考得差 冇大學讀都唔緊要<br />\n好多路可以兜番上去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年15分既我入到asso都係墊屍底<br />\n而家都好地地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以上黎啦 等我地比溫暖大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de108f09f94554c663d046baf82d0b4e334cd095","tid":1302002,"uid":214482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zJBpZ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zJBpZ9.png&h=a0f83e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報讀非本地高等及專業教育課程前，注意該課程是否經已辦理註冊或豁免註冊及相應的資歷架構級別。切勿一次繳交全部學費。要索取並保留學費收據。如有疑問，請到教育局網站查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplications.edb.gov.hk%2Fncr%2Fncr.aspx%3Flangno%3D2%26searchtype%3D3&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=4c221fd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局關心您。"},{"pid":"4f73a57bb54448cc3cd6480af6912769831d901f","tid":1302002,"uid":233208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T23:19:52.000Z","msg":"我vtc有土木工程嘅offer,算唔算ive <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828678ebebb33b134b750b7ec54c32b621f0f9c7","tid":1302002,"uid":71930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":